original: Håkansson, Sven Hugo, kyrkoherde, Skärlöv, f. 7/2/03 i Ahnundsryd, Kronob. k, av Elof H. o. Matilda Svensson. G. 40 m. Elin Andersson. Barn: Stefan f. 41, B.ritt-Marie 44, Örjan 47. — Stud: ex. i Lund 22, kansiliex. där 24, teol. fil. ex,. 29, teol. kanid., prakt, teoil. prov samt prästv. f. Växjö stift 32. Pastorsadj. i Villstad 32-33’, v. pastor där 33-34, i Vederslöv 34-3’5, Böda 35-36, Hulter-stad 36-37, kyrkoh. i Hulterstad o. Stenåsa sed. 37. Ordf. i skolstyr. o. ky rko s tämmo r.
translated: Håkansson, Sven Hugo, vicar, Skärlöv, b. Feb. 7, 1903 in Ahnundsryd, Kronobergs län, son of Elof H. and Matilda Svensson. Married in 1940 to Elin Andersson. Children: Stefan b. 1941, Britt-Marie b. 1944, Örjan b. 1947. Education: graduated from Lund University in 1922, civil servant exam there in 1924, bachelor's degree in theology in 1929, theological candidate, practical theological exam and ordained in Växjö diocese in 1932. Pastor's assistant in Villstad from 1932-1933, assistant pastor there from 1933-1934, in Vederslöv from 1934-1935, Böda from 1935-1936, Hulterstad from 1936-1937, vicar in Hulterstad and Stenåsa since 1937. Chairman of the school board and church council.

education.name: civil servant exam at Lund University
